---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Mi Rancho — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Mi Rancho deployed six robotic palletizers across four tortilla lines (plus one on the chip line) on Formic's Robots-as-a-Service model — solving safety and turnover amid 40%+ annual growth."
  ogTitle="Mi Rancho — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="7 palletizers · 40%+ annual growth · zero capital"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/mi-rancho" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Mi Rancho
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Mi Rancho</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">Mi Rancho Makes Production Leap with Automated Stacking of Millions of Tortillas per Year</h1>
    <p class="lede">Growing 40%+ a year out of a 150,000-sq-ft Elk Grove plant, Mi Rancho put six robotic palletizers on its tortilla lines — plus one on the chip line — and made safety, not headcount, the constraint it solved.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/mi-rancho-hero.jpg" alt="Mi Rancho robotic palletizing on the tortilla line" />
      <span class="dv-cap">Mi Rancho · Elk Grove, CA</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Founded</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">1939</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Elk Grove, CA</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Tortillas, chips, salsas</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Facility</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">150,000 sq ft</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Growth</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">40%+ YoY</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Formic systems</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">7 palletizers</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>Growth you can't <em>hire your way through</em>.</h2>
      <p>Mi Rancho produces millions of pounds of goods a year with 40%+ year-over-year growth from a 150,000-sq-ft facility in Elk Grove, California. Senior Director of Operations Joe Santana points to labor shortage, manual-stacking safety, and turnover as the core challenges — the workers simply aren't out there to hire fast enough.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Millions of pounds a year, 40%+ annual growth</li>
        <li>Manual end-of-line stacking a real safety concern</li>
        <li>Hard to hire and retain for the heaviest jobs</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/mi-rancho-2.jpg" alt="Mi Rancho production line and palletizing" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Tortilla & chip lines</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0095.jpg" alt="Formic robotic palletizer on a packaging line" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">RaaS · $0 capital</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Six on tortillas, <em>one on chips</em>.</h2>
      <p>Mi Rancho deployed six robotic palletizers across four tortilla lines, plus one industrial palletizer on the chip line — all on Formic's Robots-as-a-Service model. That meant zero capital, hourly usage pricing, and 24/7 monitoring, maintenance, and upgrades, with no need to hire a robotics team to own it.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>6 robotic palletizers across 4 tortilla lines</li>
        <li>+1 industrial palletizer on the chip line</li>
        <li>RaaS: $0 capital, 24/7 monitoring and maintenance</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"We want people to come to work, and we want them to go home wholesome. We don't want them to be injured, and so the only way to protect them is if we find other ways to do the job. Lifting boxes is something that robots can easily do."</blockquote>
      <cite>Joe Santana · Senior Director of Operations, Mi Rancho</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">Safer line. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">No idle CapEx.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">7</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Palletizers deployed</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">4</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Tortilla lines automated</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">40%+</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Annual growth supported</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Make your <em>production leap</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
